Riema Attribution Notice

Riema is an original pure-Lua environment manager implementation.

Riema is inspired by the Hererocks project and follows the general problem
space pioneered by that tool: building isolated Lua and LuaRocks environments.

Hererocks was created by Peter Melnichenko and distributed under the MIT
license. Copyright (c) Peter Melnichenko

Riema does not reuse the Hererocks Python implementation. This repository is a
clean Lua rewrite with its own command structure, data model, and source code.
